WEBVTT

00:00.890 --> 00:03.724
<i>- Previously on</i> The Resident...
- If I hadn't gotten injured,

00:03.725 --> 00:05.783
they might not have
caught my cancer in time.

00:05.784 --> 00:08.345
- Your supplements have potential.
- You killed my pitch.

00:08.346 --> 00:11.539
- You said Chastain doesn't take chances.
- They don't.

00:11.540 --> 00:12.891
<i>- I do.
- AUSTIN: So what's your plan</i>

00:12.892 --> 00:15.042
if Adaku's baby becomes
your responsibility?

00:15.043 --> 00:16.621
<i>MINA: I don't have one.</i>

00:16.622 --> 00:19.213
<i>CAIN: Hawkins is</i> a whistle-blower.
He's a threat to the hospital.

00:19.214 --> 00:22.457
I'll handle it. Dr. Hawkins,
you lied to the transplant board.

00:22.458 --> 00:24.925
You're fired. Give me your pager.

00:27.430 --> 00:28.530
Thank you.

00:30.795 --> 00:32.101
<i>MAN: We're a high-volume outfit.</i>

00:32.101 --> 00:34.320
A lot of kitchen mishaps
and food poisoning.

00:34.321 --> 00:36.080
Waiting room's packed 24/7,

00:36.081 --> 00:38.658
- so ten minutes per patient.
- And if the diagnosis

00:38.659 --> 00:40.419
isn't obvious, and it
takes over ten minutes?

00:44.258 --> 00:46.041
We also take pride in
customer satisfaction.

00:46.042 --> 00:47.617
Your bonuses are tied to it.

00:47.618 --> 00:49.469
So... flexible prescribing,

00:49.470 --> 00:50.971
- if you know what I mean.
- (LAUGHS)

00:50.972 --> 00:52.622
Patients hate being told "no".

00:52.623 --> 00:54.215
Yeah. Isn't that what contributed

00:54.216 --> 00:56.220
- to the opioid crisis?
- (CHUCKLES)

00:56.221 --> 00:58.364
And <i> why</i> did you say
you're not at Chastain anymore?

01:02.855 --> 01:05.337
<i>CONRAD: If it were easy,
everyone would be a doctor,</i>

01:05.339 --> 01:08.431
<i>because this is the best job in
the world, despite everything.</i>

01:08.432 --> 01:10.011
Because <i> of everything.</i>

01:10.012 --> 01:11.888
<i>FLECK: How you feeling?</i>

01:11.889 --> 01:14.866
<i>NIGEL: Pain-free.
First time in over a decade.</i>

01:14.867 --> 01:17.035
<i>CONRAD: The transplant
team has been called in.</i>

01:17.036 --> 01:19.187
<i>I will be with you
every step of the way.</i>

01:19.188 --> 01:22.874
(IMITATING POLICE SIREN)

01:22.875 --> 01:25.543
(PHONE BUZZING)

01:28.680 --> 01:31.458
_

01:31.459 --> 01:34.294
(SIGHS)

01:34.295 --> 01:36.827
<i>CONRAD: I spent half my
life without a father.</i>

01:36.828 --> 01:39.248
<i>MARSHALL: We're gonna fix that.</i>

01:39.249 --> 01:41.751
<i>DEVON: These patients need you,</i>

01:41.752 --> 01:45.271
<i>and I think this hospital
needs doctors like both of us.</i>

01:51.011 --> 01:53.480
<i>CONRAD: God, I love
when you believe in me.</i>

01:53.481 --> 01:55.865
<i>NIC: I never stopped believing in you.</i>

